in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/selectionchange_event\"><code>selectionchange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Document/selectstart_event\"><code>selectstart</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchcancel_event\"><code>touchcancel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchend_event\"><code>touchend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchmove_event\"><code>touchmove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchstart_event\"><code>touchstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/visibilitychange_event\"><code>visibilitychange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herencia</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a DOM</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortController\"><code>AbortController</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbortSignal\"><code>AbortSignal</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/AbstractRange\"><code>AbstractRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Attr\"><code>Attr</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CDATASection\"><code>CDATASection</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CharacterData\"><code>CharacterData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Comment\"><code>Comment</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/CustomEvent\"><code>CustomEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DOMError\"><code>DOMError</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DomException\"><code>DOMException</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMImplementation\"><code>DOMImplementation</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DOMParser\"><code>DOMParser</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPoint\"><code>DOMPoint</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMPointReadOnly\"><code>DOMPointReadOnly</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMRect\"><code>DOMRect</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTimeStamp\"><code>DOMTimeStamp</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DOMTokenList\"><code>DOMTokenList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/DocumentFragment\"><code>DocumentFragment</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/DocumentType\"><code>DocumentType</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/HTMLCollection\"><code>HTMLCollection</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/MutationObserver\"><code>MutationObserver</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NamedNodeMap\"><code>NamedNodeMap</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/NodeIterator\"><code>NodeIterator</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/NodeList\"><code>NodeList</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProcessingInstruction\"><code>ProcessingInstruction</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/API/Range\"><code>Range</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/StaticRange\"><code>StaticRange</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Text\"><code>Text</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextDecoder\"><code>TextDecoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TextEncoder\"><code>TextEncoder</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TimeRanges\"><code>TimeRanges</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/TreeWalker\"><code>TreeWalker</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLDocument\"><code>XMLDocument</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\">Devuelve&nbsp;el primer elemento del documento (utilizando un <a href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tree_traversal#Pre-order_2\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">recorrido primero en profundidad pre ordenado</a> de los nodos del documento) que coincida&nbsp;con el grupo especificado de selectores.</div>\n\n<div id=\"sect3\">&nbsp;</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>element <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>selectores<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Donde:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><code>element</code>&nbsp;es un objeto de tipo&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element\" title=\"en-US/docs/DOM/element\">element</a>.</li>\n <li><code>selectores</code>&nbsp;es una cadena de caracteres que contiene uno o más <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Learn/CSS/Building_blocks/Selectors\">selectores CSS</a>&nbsp;separados por coma.</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example","title":"Ejemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>En este ejemplo, obtendremos el primer elemento del documento con la clase \"miClase\":</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> el <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\".miClase\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes","title":"Ejemplo más útil","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Los <em>Selectores</em> pueden ser muy útiles como se demostrará en el siguiente ejemplo. Aquí, será retornado el primer elemento <code>&lt;input name=\"login\" /&gt;</code> dentro de <code>&lt;div class=\"user-panel main\"&gt;</code>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> el <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"div.user-panel.main input[name='login']\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notes_2","title":"Notas","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Devuelve&nbsp;<code>null</code>&nbsp;si no se encuentran coincidencias, de lo contrario, retorna el primer elemento&nbsp;&nbsp;encontrado.</li>\n <li>Si el selector coincide con un ID y este ID es usado erróneamente varias veces en el documento, devuelve el primer elemento encontrado.</li>\n <li>Lanza una excepción de tipo SYNTAX_ERR si el grupo de selectores especificado no es válido.</li>\n <li><span style=\"font-family: Consolas,Monaco,'Andale Mono',monospace;\">querySelector() se introdujo en la <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/selectors-api/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">API Selectors</a>.</span></li>\n <li>La cadena de caracteres que se pasa&nbsp;como argumento a <code><span style=\"font-family: Consolas,Monaco,'Andale Mono',monospace;\">querySelector debe seguir la sintaxis CSS.</span></code></li>\n <li>Las Pseudo-clases CSS nunca devolverán elementos, tal y como está&nbsp;especificado en la <code><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/selectors-api/#grammar\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">AP​I Selectors</a></code>.</li>\n <li>Para que coincidan ID's o selectores que no siguen la sintáxis CSS (usando inapropiadamente dos puntos o un espacio por ejemplo), se debe 'escapar' el carácter con una barra invertida (\\). Como la barra invertida es un carácter de 'escape' en JavaScript, si estás indicando una cadena de caracteres literal, debes 'escaparla' dos veces (una para la cadena de caracteres JavaScript y otra para el querySelector):&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>foo\\bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>foo:bar<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token script\"><span class=\"token language-javascript\">\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#foo\\bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>               <span class=\"token comment\">// \"#fooar\"</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#foo\\bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// No coincide con nada</span>\n\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#foo\\\\bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>              <span class=\"token comment\">// \"#foo\\bar\"</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#foo\\\\\\\\bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>            <span class=\"token comment\">// \"#foo\\\\bar\"</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#foo\\\\\\\\bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// Coincide con el primer div</span>\n\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#foo:bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>    <span class=\"token comment\">// No coincide con nada</span>\n  document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'#foo\\\\:bar'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// Coincide con el segundo div</span>\n</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidad&nbsp;en los navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Plataforma</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari (WebKit)</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Soporte Basico</td>\n   <td>1</td>\n   <td>3.5 (1.9.1)<br>\n    <a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=416317\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">error&nbsp;416317</a></td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td>10</td>\n   <td>3.2 (525.3)<br>\n    <a rel=\"external noopener\" href=\"https://bugs.webkit.org/show_bug.cgi?id=16587\" class=\"external\" title=\"\">WebKit bug 16587</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Plataforma</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE 